<div class="section">
    <h2>Fuentes para Piezas Descartadas/Obsoletas Baratas</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Subastas Salvage (para paneles/wheels/interiores con defectos cosméticos)</strong>: <a href="https://www.copart.com/">Copart</a> | <a href="https://www.iaai.com/">IAAI</a> | <a href="https://sca.auction/">SCA Auction</a> (busca "minor damage" o "cosmetic only").</li>
        <li><strong>Surplus/Obsolete Auto Parts</strong>: <a href="https://www.car-part.com/">Car-Part.com</a> | <a href="https://autopartsobsolete.com/">Auto Parts Obsolete</a> | <a href="https://jbrsurplusautoparts.com/">JBR Surplus</a>.</li>
        <li><strong>Repurposed EV Parts (baterías/motores usados/obsoletos pero funcionales)</strong>: <a href="https://www.thunderstruck-ev.com/garage-sale/">Thunderstruck EV Garage Sale</a> | <a href="https://greentecauto.com/product-category/repurposed-batteries/">Greentec Auto Repurposed</a> | <a href="https://ingenext.ca/">Ingenext Used EV Parts</a> | <a href="https://www.secondlife-evbatteries.com/">Second Life EV Batteries</a>.</li>
        <li><strong>Para Sodium-Ion</strong>: Aún emergente (2025 producción masiva CATL/HiNa), busca surplus en Alibaba o second-life pronto.</li>
    </ul>
</div>

